description:
So ask yourself why local health agencies who are not elected officials are making these decisions. 
Check the chart for US deaths from COVID 19 (even though we know they have been padding the numbers) 18,747 ! How many died last year from the seasonal flu?? 80,000. How many died in 2019 from cancer ? 606,880 !  Why don’t they close McDonald, why don’t they ban known carcinogens like food dyes and TBHQ? 
Because they don’t care.  This is about control not concern for health. Stop letting your freedom and our countries solvency slip through our fingers!
